rows.name:
I tell my daughter many stories
about when I was young, mo.

rows.label: tlk4240005101_msg0002
rows.name:
The fun times, the happy times,
the time I got burned playing with fire at night...

rows.label: tlk4240005101_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a mother's duty to teach her daughter
about embarrassing experiences so she can
learn from them, mo.
